<p><strong><em>Angelic Weapons.</em></strong> The planetarâ€™s weapon attacks are magical. When the planetar hits with any weapon, the weapon deals an extra 5d8 radiant damage (included in the attack).</p>

<p><strong><em>Divine Awareness.</em></strong> The planetar knows if it hears a lie.</p>

<p><strong><em>Innate Spellcasting.</em></strong> The planetarâ€™s spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC 20). The planetar can innately cast the following spells, requiring no material components:</p>

